    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it basically looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! The paint is glowing, the interior is spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I know you\u2019re going to fall in love the second you see it. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants that brand-new feel without the brand-new price tag. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014I can't wait to find it a great new home!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
