      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS timing. Meticulously maintained, the chassis exhibits zero subframe fatigue, and the rod bearing service has been preemptively completed to factory tolerances. Power is transferred via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Suspension geometry remains true with fresh bushings and original Sachs dampers, providing the precise, communicative steering rack feel these cars are famed for. No pixel degradation in the cluster or bolster wear on the Nappa leather; this is a true collector-quality driver's machine.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
